README for differential histone modification analyiss using DiffBind

DiffBind links
	- http://bioconductor.org/packages/release/bioc/html/DiffBind.html
	- http://bioconductor.org/packages/release/bioc/vignettes/DiffBind/inst/doc/DiffBind.pdf
	- http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v481/n7381/full/nature10730.html

Required inputs are:
	- input CSV file:
	  -- histone ChIPseq BAM file
	  -- control BAM file (input, IGG, H3 ...)
	  -- histone peak regions in 3 column BED format

USAGE

	R -f /path/to/scripts/histoneNod/diffBind_histoneMod.R
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
NOTES
	- no file checks are performed
